emuInput.TitMainTitle: Sign for Armour Star Choice Beef, on wall of New Diamond Market above door with exit sign, neon signs advertising meat products to left and right
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 22, 1955, pg. 12, reads: "New Diamond Market -...The management of the New Diamond Market welcomes you to share in their giant twenty-fifth anniversary celebration beginning Friday, Oct. 21, through Dec. 6 - Harris Photo."
